title: Murphy, Escobar become the latest surprise stars in October
text: > Sports Murphy, Escobar become the latest surprise stars in October FILE- In this Oct. 21, 2010, file photo, San Francisco Giants' Cody Ross hits a run-scoring double during the fourth inning of Game 5 of baseball's National League Championship Series against the Philadelphia Phillies in San Francisco. Ross went from unwanted man in August to MVP of the NLCS with an impressive power display against the Phillies' Big Three of Roy Halladay, Roy Oswalt and Cole Hamels. (AP Photo/Marcio Jose Sanchez, File)
